Direct Known Subclasses:
ChatGUI, EndGUI, LoginGUI
public abstract class GUIPass
extends com.jme.renderer.pass.Pass

GUIPass renders FengGUI widgets in its own separate RenderPass to enhance performance and scene graph management.

GUIPass has to be added to a BasicPassManager after the root RenderPass and before any additional special effect RenderPass such as BloomRenderPass or ShadowRenderPass.

Subclasses which extends GUIPass need to implement initialize method to create all GUI widgets and add them to the Display.

GUIPass automatically invokes IInputConverter to set the FengGUI Display instance for input conversion.
